PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1771812211
OL,3,CEvidence around unsolved murder of
OL,4,CGlasgow man Alexander Blue under review
OL,6,FBilly, 67, said: "What was horrendous
OL,7,Fwas my mother lost her son, and that's
OL,8,Falways been my driving force.
OL,10,F"She's never got over that. She'll
OL,11,Fnever get over what happened that day."
OL,13,FBilly says the looming 25-year
OL,14,Fanniversary of Alexander's death may
OL,15,Fspur the police on to take more action
OL,16,Fon the case.
OL,26,@nD@ROUrD@AOUsD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1771812211
OL,3,CEvidence around unsolved murder of
OL,4,CGlasgow man Alexander Blue under review
OL,6,FHe has had recent meetings with police
OL,7,Fand Crown Office officials including
OL,8,Fthe Lord Advocate Dorothy Bain KC.
OL,9,FBoth agencies have promised to keep
OL,10,Fhim updated.
OL,12,FHe said: "I think they know what's
OL,13,Fcoming in about 18 months, if they get
OL,14,Fto that point with total failure.
OL,16,F"The fact that nobody's been charged
OL,17,Fwith murder is a disappointment.
OL,19,F"But the fact that nobody's been
OL,20,Fcharged with anything related to that
OL,21,Fmurder is an absolute disgrace."
OL,26,@tD@JOUxD@AOU{D@AOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1771812211
OL,3,CEvidence around unsolved murder of
OL,4,CGlasgow man Alexander Blue under review
OL,6,FHe was critical of Police Scotland,
OL,7,Fsaying his family has been treated
OL,8,Flike "garbage" for years.
OL,10,FThe Crown Office said it works closely
OL,11,Fwith the police to review unresolved
OL,12,Fhomicides to ascertain if there are
OL,13,Fany new evidential developments.
OL,15,FA spokesman said: "The Crown Office
OL,16,Fand Procurator Fiscal Service
OL,17,Frecognise the suffering of families
OL,18,Fwho have been denied justice.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@NO]wD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1771812211
OL,3,CEvidence around unsolved murder of
OL,4,CGlasgow man Alexander Blue under review
OL,6,F"The murder of Alexander Blue remains
OL,7,Fan unresolved homicide and we are
OL,8,Fabsolutely committed to reviewing such
OL,9,Fcases along with Police Scotland.
OL,11,F"Unresolved homicides are never
OL,12,Fclosed, and we work closely with
OL,13,Fpolice to explore any new evidential
OL,14,Fdevelopments which would allow us to
OL,15,Fbring such cases to court.
OL,17,F"The Blue family will continue to be
OL,18,Fkept informed should any significant
OL,19,Fdevelopments come to light."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1771812211
OL,3,CEvidence around unsolved murder of
OL,4,CGlasgow man Alexander Blue under review
OL,6,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"This is obviously still a difficult
OL,8,Ftime for the Blue family who have
OL,9,Fsuffered distress and heartache over
OL,10,Fthe last two decades as they seek
OL,11,Fanswers and justice for Alexander.
OL,13,F"Police Scotland never considers cases
OL,14,Fclosed and this case remains under
OL,15,Freview. There is no barrier over the
OL,16,Fpassage of time to the investigation
OL,17,Fof unresolved homicide cases.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1771812211
OL,3,CEvidence around unsolved murder of
OL,4,CGlasgow man Alexander Blue under review
OL,6,F"Homicide Governance and Review
OL,7,Factively keeps all undetected and
OL,8,Funresolved homicides under review and
OL,9,Fmeets regularly with the Crown Office
OL,10,Fand Procurator Fiscal Service in an
OL,11,Fattempt to review these cases and
OL,12,Fpursue resolution. We will continue to
OL,13,Fupdate the families of the victims of
OL,14,Fsuch crimes with any new developments,
OL,15,Fwhere appropriate.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1771812211
OL,3,CEvidence around unsolved murder of
OL,4,CGlasgow man Alexander Blue under review
OL,6,F"Police Scotland along with our
OL,7,Fpartners in the Scottish Police
OL,8,FAuthority Forensic Services, continue
OL,9,Fto relentlessly pursue advances in
OL,10,Ftechnology and investigative
OL,11,Fapproaches which help bring those
OL,12,Fresponsible for serious and violent
OL,13,Fcrimes to justice and provide answers
OL,14,Ffor families of the victims of such
OL,15,Fcrimes.
OL,17,F"Scientific and forensic developments,
OL,18,Fcombined with information from the
OL,19,Fpublic and determined investigative
OL,20,Fwork can yield new opportunities in
OL,21,Fsuch cases."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU}D@LO]
